data.description: Beautiful home in Alamo Ranch! Elegant entry, formal dining room. Kitchen features granite counter tops and a bar flowing into the breakfast area and living room. Guest bedroom/second master and full bath is located on the main level. Secondary beds with walk in closets, game room, and master located upstairs. Primary Suite is spacious offering high ceilings and windows for natural light. Master bathroom very roomy with a double vanity sink, garden tub, and stand alone shower. Recent carpet replacement and interior paint!  Backyard has a covered patio with a hot tub fully fenced in with a privacy fence making the home great for entertainment! Home is located near Lackland Air Force Base, Alamo Ranch Shopping Center, eateries, entertainment, and Seaworld and is located just outside the city limits to save on property taxes!
